            "color": "sky",
            "description": "–ó <strong>will/would</strong> –ī–Ľ—Ź –ľ–į–Ļ–Ī—É—ā–Ĺ—Ė—Ö –ī—Ė–Ļ –į–Ī–ĺ –Ī–į–∂–į–Ĺ—Ć:",
            "examples": [
                {
                    "en": "Will you come by car or by bus?",
                    "ua": "Will they arrive in the morning or afternoon? write?"
                },
                {
